  <entry>
    <title>Remove &lt;wbr&gt; tags from Beautiful Soup object</title>
    <link href="http://luminoid.github.io/blog/2017/06/06/Remove-wbr-tags-from-Beautiful-Soup-object/"/>
    <id>http://luminoid.github.io/blog/2017/06/06/Remove-wbr-tags-from-Beautiful-Soup-object/</id>
    <published>2017-06-06T04:35:16.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-06-09T05:14:45.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Goal"><a href="#Goal" class="headerlink" title="Goal"></a>Goal</h2><p>Get plain text from a Beautiful Soup object with <code>&lt;br /&gt;</code> converted into line break and <code>&lt;wbr /&gt;</code> ignored.</p>
<h2 id="Code"><a href="#Code" class="headerlink" title="Code"></a>Code</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> re</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> bs4 <span class="keyword">import</span> BeautifulSoup</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">html = <span class="string">"""</span></div><div class="line">&lt;span&gt;</div><div class="line">    Here is some text.</div><div class="line">    Here is some other text with a line break in it. &lt;br/&gt;And it should be divided into two lines.</div><div class="line">    This line, &lt;wbr /&gt;contains some word break opportunities, &lt;wbr /&gt;which should be ignored. &lt;wbr/&gt;And the output should be in one line.</div><div class="line">&lt;span/&gt;</div><div class="line">"""</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">soup = BeautifulSoup(html, <span class="string">'html.parser'</span>)</div><div class="line">tag = soup.find(<span class="string">'span'</span>)</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="comment"># remove &lt;wbr&gt; tags</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> wbr <span class="keyword">in</span> soup.findAll(<span class="string">'wbr'</span>):</div><div class="line">    wbr_previous = wbr.previous_sibling</div><div class="line">    wbr_next = wbr.next_sibling</div><div class="line">    wbr_previous.string.replace_with(wbr_previous + wbr_next)</div><div class="line">    wbr.extract()</div><div class="line">    wbr_next.extract()</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="comment"># reformat the text</span></div><div class="line">content = re.sub(<span class="string">r'\s*?\n+\s*'</span>, <span class="string">'\n'</span>, tag.get_text(<span class="string">'\n'</span>))</div><div class="line">print(content)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<a id="more"></a>
<p><strong>Result:</strong><br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">Here is some text.</div><div class="line">Here is some other text with a line break in it.</div><div class="line">And it should be divided into two lines.</div><div class="line">This line, contains some word break opportunities, which should be ignored. And the output should be in one line.</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;h2 id=&quot;Goal&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#Goal&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;Goal&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Goal&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Get plain text from a Beautiful Soup object with &lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;br /&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt; converted into line break and &lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;wbr /&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt; ignored.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;Code&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#Code&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;Code&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Code&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight python&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;2&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;3&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;4&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;5&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;6&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;7&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;8&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;9&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;10&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;11&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;12&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;13&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;14&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;15&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;16&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;17&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;18&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;19&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;20&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;21&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;22&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;23&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;24&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;25&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; re&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;from&lt;/span&gt; bs4 &lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; BeautifulSoup&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;html = &lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&quot;&quot;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;span&amp;gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;    Here is some text.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;    Here is some other text with a line break in it. &amp;lt;br/&amp;gt;And it should be divided into two lines.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;    This line, &amp;lt;wbr /&amp;gt;contains some word break opportunities, &amp;lt;wbr /&amp;gt;which should be ignored. &amp;lt;wbr/&amp;gt;And the output should be in one line.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;span/&amp;gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&quot;&quot;&quot;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;soup = BeautifulSoup(html, &lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&#39;html.parser&#39;&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;tag = soup.find(&lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&#39;span&#39;&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;comment&quot;&gt;# remove &amp;lt;wbr&amp;gt; tags&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; wbr &lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; soup.findAll(&lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&#39;wbr&#39;&lt;/span&gt;):&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;    wbr_previous = wbr.previous_sibling&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;    wbr_next = wbr.next_sibling&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;    wbr_previous.string.replace_with(wbr_previous + wbr_next)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;    wbr.extract()&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;    wbr_next.extract()&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;comment&quot;&gt;# reformat the text&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;content = re.sub(&lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;r&#39;\s*?\n+\s*&#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&#39;\n&#39;&lt;/span&gt;, tag.get_text(&lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&#39;\n&#39;&lt;/span&gt;))&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;print(content)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
